## How we work

- **Communication:** We default to async. Use email for non-urgent items.
- **Meetings:** Keep them short. Every meeting has an agenda.
- **Files:** Everything lives in Nextcloud under `/shared/`. No email attachments.
- **Decisions:** Document them. If it isn't written down, it didn't happen.

